Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.59,0:00:20.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(悟)あっ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.30,0:00:24.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.91,0:00:25.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,《あいつだ》
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.14,0:00:29.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It can't end here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.92,0:00:30.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,《終われない》
